Detection: Attacker Tool - Quasar Remote Access Tool (RAT)

Reference: Covers all potatoes - Petit, Juicy, Lovely, Local, God, Rotten
PoC tool to coerce Windows hosts to authenticate to other machines via MS-EFSRPC EfsRpcOpenFileRaw or other functions.
PuTTy / SSH tools outside Program Files is highly suspicious.
